      "message": "Use of http.DefaultClient causes the state of the returned ServerConfig shared across all tests.\n\nAt L37 in artifact_channel_test.go, it overrides cfg.Client.Transport with a mock transport.\n\n```\ncfg.ArtifactUploader.Client.Transport \u003d \u0026mockTransport{func(req *http.Request) (*http.Response, error) {\n    do_something()\n}\n```\n\nIt unexpectedly affects other unit tests with testServerConfig(), because the custom mockTransport{} set in artifact_channel_test.go is being used by all other tests launched after the test.",
